    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject is 18-64 years of age

          -  Subject is female

          -  Subject is pregnant and between 6 and 16 weeks of gestation

          -  Subject provides a signed and dated informed consent

          -  If subject undergoes a routine ultrasound between weeks 16 and 28, she agrees to
             provide the fetal sex results

          -  If subject undergoes an invasive procedure, she agrees to provide the fetal sex
             results

        Exclusion Criteria:
      </textblock>
